Highlights of the day's news.(SABC)Get the latest News as it happens on the SABC News Live Blog. WATCH: Minister Nathi Mthethwa pays tribute to Lundi Tyamara Thousands have paid tribute to the late gospel star Lundi Tyamara in song at his funeral in Worcester in the Boland. The celebrated 38-year-old musician released 16 albums during his lifetime. Arts and culture minister Nathi Mthethwa delivered the keynote address.